cc:Work.dc:title: Elvie #065
cc:Work.dc:description:
[Panel 1: Elvie is holding a card and pen]
Elvie: Janet's leaving the company, but I'm the last person to write in her card.
Everyone else has already written the things I wanted to say.
Hmmm… Perhaps there is still something I can write…
[Panel 2: Close-up of card reveals lots of kind comments from other staff members, and Elvie's message]
Elvie (written message): CTRL-A. CTRL-C. CTRL-V.
